#summary Search for wildernesses of barbarian camps

*Search for:*
  A dropdown-box for selecting whether to search for Barbarian Camps or Wildernesses
*Center: X: xxx Y: yyy*
  Enter the coordinates for the center of your desired search area or click one of the _city buttons_ http://i.imgur.com/MPlZr.png to center on that city. 

*Max. Distance: xx*
  Tells the Bot how far to search from the desired center. Max Distance must be between 1 and 75.

*Start Search*
  Button to initiate the map-scan.
----

You will get a table when the search is done:
|| *Location* || *Distance* || *Lvl* || *Type* ||
|| xxx,yyy || 8.00 || 5 || Lake ||
|| xxx,yyy || 12.12 || 3 || Grassland ||
|| xxx,yyy || 13.87 || 3 || Mountain ||

----

To the right of the table you get filtering settings:
||Min. level to show:||If you don't want to see _low_ level Wildernesses or Camps.||
||Max. level to show:||If you don't want to see _high_ level Wildernesses or Camps.||
||Wilderness Type:^*^ ||Lets you filter for one _type_ of wildernesses.||
||Unowned Only:^*^ ||If checked the table displays only _unowned_ wildernesses.||
||Sort By:||Lets you sort the table by _Level_ or _Distance_ from center.||
||Show coords only:||If checked the table only displays the _Location_ column.||

^*^  not available when searching for Barbarian Camps
----
If _KOCAttack_ or _KOCAttack - Extra Features!_ are installed and running another button will appear beneath the filtering settings when searching for Barbarian Camps:

|| <font color="c0c000" > Export Results ||

This button opens: _Power Bot Export_ dialog which contains a export table:
||Target Type||# targets||STroops||Wagon||Archers||Cavalry||Heavies||Ballista||
||Barb level 1|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 2|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 3|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 4|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 5|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 6|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 7|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 8|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 9|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||
||Barb level 10|| xx ||0||0||0||0||0||0||

The Barbarian Camps from the _filtered list_ is displayed in this new table sorted as amount of targets for each level/type of Barbarian Camp. In the table you can enter how many troops of each kind you want so send to _each_ Camp. 

When you have populated the table as you want it you should press the button at the bottom of the page:

|| <font color="c0c000" > Bulk Add to KOC Attack ||

This button start exporting the attack to the city you centered on if you used the _city buttons_ http://i.imgur.com/MPlZr.png or to the city currently selected in the game. Each level populated in the table gets exported in ascending order of level. After each level exported you get a popup with the message "Bulk added xx coords" and a "OK" button. Then it exports the next level. After the exports it shows the table and have added a log beneath the _Bulk Add to KOC Attack_ button. The export is done and you can close the dialog.

